    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_1932547265090702594.png",
                "id": "talent31931",
                "key": "我流剑术",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "我流剑术"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">乱岚拨止</span>。</p><p>如果此技能引发了扩散，则将<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">乱岚拨止</span>转换为被扩散的元素。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此技能结算后：</span>我方切换到后一个角色。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/33d0a2ad4ba893402e879d35ab6ce233_5576466361441814859.png",
                "id": "talent85070",
                "key": "千早振",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "千早振"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">流风秋野</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/3b2e6b2c4ffbc7d13d7f2461cb4497e9_3541527972246630338.png",
                "id": "talent7426",
                "key": "万叶之一刀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "万叶之一刀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色或召唤物引发扩散反应后：</span>转换此牌的元素类型，改为造成被扩散的元素类型的伤害。（离场前仅限一次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_365197506558469948.png",
                "id": "talent52849",
                "key": "流风秋野",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/f67510fea70ff0f59b3b627d297f30fc_8849458133864433756.gif",
                "title": "流风秋野"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷元素伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_2053633160181002816.png",
                "id": "talent80499",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">乱岚拨止</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所属角色进行下落攻击时：</span>造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>转变为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，且伤害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">角色使用技能后：</span>移除此效果。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">下落攻击</span></strong></p><p>角色被切换为「出战角色」后，本回合内的下一个战斗行动若为「普通攻击」，则被被视为「下落攻击」。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/13/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8924109586523453296.png",
